Definition: tall North American perennial with creeping rootstocks and narrow leaves and spikes of pinkish-purple flowers occurring in great abundance in burned-over areas or recent clearings
Example: an important honey plant
Synonyms: giant_willowherb, rosebay_willowherb, wickup, Epilobium_angustifolium, willowherb, genus_Epilobium, m, tall, North, American, perennial, with, creeping, rootstocks, and, narrow, leaves, spikes, of, pinkish-purple, flowers, occurring, in, great, abundance, burned-over, areas, or, recent, clearings, an, important, honey, plant
Category: noun.plant
